      "span_text": "The syntax of a query is http://1kgenome.exascale. info/ mode ?xstart= x1 & xend= x2 &ystart= y1 &yend= y2 &zstart= z1 &zend= z2 , where <mode> should be replaced by js test to query the model from (11), or 3D to query the model from [CITATION_1] . <x1> to <z2> indicate the spatial coordinate of the cell."
